                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241202-89-off481 t18241202-89-cd482"></join>, a handkerchief, value 6 d., from the person of a 
                     <persName id="t18241202-89-victim526" type="victimName">man whose name is unknown<interp inst="t18241202-89-victim526" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
